verbose_text: In fact, olive oil is characterized by a unique fatty acid composition (very high level of oleic acid and a low ratio (omega-6)/(omega-3) polyunsaturated FA), which in the combination with oleuropein aglycone provide marked down-regulation of a proto-oncogenic HER2.
